OL,3,CThe tiny robot which could
OL,4,Crevolutionise cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FA tiny magnetic robot which can take
OL,7,F3D scans deep within the body could
OL,8,Frevolutionise early cancer detection,
OL,9,Fresearchers say.
OL,11,FA team of engineers from the
OL,12,FUniversity of Leeds say the robots
OL,13,Fprovide the first high-resolution
OL,14,Fultrasound images inside the
OL,15,Fgastrointestinal tract, or gut.
OL,17,FAcademics say it paves the way to
OL,18,Ftransform the diagnosis and treatment
OL,19,Fof several forms of cancer by enabling
OL,20,F"virtual", non-invasive biopsies.
