OL,3,CThe tiny robot which could
OL,4,Crevolutionise cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FPietro Valdastri, who coordinated the
OL,7,Fresearch, said: "For the first time,
OL,8,Fthis research enables us to
OL,9,Freconstruct a 3D ultrasound image
OL,10,Ftaken from a probe deep inside the gut.
OL,12,F"This approach enables in-situ tissue
OL,13,Fanalysis and diagnosis of colorectal
OL,14,Fcancer, with immediate results. The
OL,15,Fprocess of diagnosing colorectal
OL,16,Fcancer currently requires a tissue
OL,17,Fsample to be removed, then sent to a
OL,18,Flab, with results taking from one to
OL,19,Fthree weeks."
