OL,3,CThe tiny robot which could
OL,4,Crevolutionise cancer diagnosis
OL,6,FPostgraduate researcher Nikita
OL,7,FGreenidge, a member of Leeds' STORM
OL,8,FLab, in the school of electronic and
OL,9,Felectrical engineering, is lead author
OL,10,Fof the paper.
OL,12,FShe said: "By combining our advanced
OL,13,Frobotics with medical ultrasound
OL,14,Fimaging, we take this innovation one
OL,15,Fstep ahead of traditional colonoscopy,
OL,16,Fallowing doctors to diagnose and treat
OL,17,Fin a single procedure ` eliminating
OL,18,Fthe wait between diagnosis and
OL,19,Fintervention.
