OL,3,CThe tiny robot which could
OL,4,Crevolutionise cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"This not only makes the process more
OL,7,Fcomfortable for patients but also
OL,8,Freduces waiting times, minimises
OL,9,Frepeat procedures, and alleviates the
OL,10,Fanxiety of waiting for potential
OL,11,Fcancer results."
OL,13,FMs Greenidge said, while the research
OL,14,Fhad been conducted in the colon, the
OL,15,Frolling properties of the oloid shape
OL,16,Fcould be applied to a variety of
OL,17,Fmagnetic medical robots, potentially
OL,18,Fexpanding its applications to other
OL,19,Fareas of the body.
