OL,3,CThe tiny robot which could
OL,4,Crevolutionise cancer diagnosis
OL,6,F"Our findings suggest new
OL,7,Fpossibilities for interdisciplinary
OL,8,Fapproaches to medical robotics,
OL,9,Fshowing how mathematical principles
OL,10,Flike simple geometry can solve real-
OL,11,Fworld healthcare challenges," she said.
